<section id="experiences" class="v3-exp">
  <div class="v3-exp-inner">
    <p class="v3-exp-overline">Experiences</p>
    <h2 class="v3-exp-title" data-aos="fade-up">The Black Sea, your way.</h2>
    <hr class="v3-hr" />
    <div class="v3-exp-grid">

      <div class="v3-exp-col">
        <div class="v3-exp-item" data-aos="fade-right">
          <div class="v3-exp-imgwrap">
            <img class="v3-exp-img v3-exp-img-portrait" src="/images/exp-forest.jpg" alt="The cliff path heading north through Strandzha forest" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <p class="v3-exp-caption">Strandzha to the north</p>
          <h3 class="v3-exp-itemhd">On the cliff path.</h3>
          <p class="v3-exp-body">The path runs north along the cliff top for eleven kilometres, passing three villages and two cape headlands before turning inland near the nature reserve at Yaylata. Start from the hotel gate at first light. Return for lunch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="v3-exp-col">
        <div class="v3-exp-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="80">
          <div class="v3-exp-imgwrap">
            <img class="v3-exp-img v3-exp-img-land" src="/images/exp-dunes.jpg" alt="One-sitting dining service at golden hour" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <p class="v3-exp-caption">One sitting. One menu.</p>
          <h3 class="v3-exp-itemhd">At the table.</h3>
          <p class="v3-exp-body">The kitchen is not a restaurant. There is one sitting, one menu per service, built from what has arrived that morning. Wine is Bulgarian. You may bring your own — we will not charge corkage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="v3-exp-item" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="140">
          <div class="v3-exp-imgwrap">
            <img class="v3-exp-img v3-exp-img-wide" src="/images/exp-sea.jpg" alt="The Black Sea from the cliff base, morning light" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <p class="v3-exp-caption">By kayak, by foot, or by swimming</p>
          <h3 class="v3-exp-itemhd">On the water.</h3>
          <p class="v3-exp-body">At the base of the cliff, accessed by a cut staircase through the rock, a simple landing dock. Kayaks for independent use. Fishing trips arranged with the men from Kamen Bryag.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
